==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˌhɝ.pɛ̆.ˈtɑ.lŏ.ʤi/
===Etymology===
Ancient Greek [[ἑρπετόν]] (herpetón) (gen. of ''reptile'') + [[-logy]] (suffix indicating a field of study or work)
===Noun===
'''her•pe•tol•o•gy'''
# the branch of [[biology]] dealing with [[reptile]]s (''Reptilia'').
